description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Chukcha purrs with a rating of 46, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 138, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, Stringalong for South, and Nine Lives for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30463-11791-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [138 Votes, Top 15% Score]
